body_html:
follow #4640 which is similar issue as this. I fixed it by removing all occurences of X86_64 bits from the build scripts compile_ios_protobuf.sh & compile_ios_tensorflow.sh and then running build_all_ios.sh
works great on device.

Note the above fix will not run on simulator
